title: Demo: Cython generator and Keras CNN
description: This notebook is taken from the excellent notebook by @ptyshevs, cnn_v2. That notebook was created for the previous challenge. My changes here were only what is needed to produce a result for the new challenge. A demonstration, if you will. The first part of the notebook uses cython to generate sample games. The NN is then trained on these samples. The given training set isn't used at all!
